Thorvald the Warrior is a fremennik council member featured in the quest The Fremennik Trials. During the quest, he tasks the player with finding and defeating the fierce warrior Koschei the Deathless. If you defeat him at least three times and die at the last form, Thorvald will vote for you. It is recommended players bring lots of food for the fight, in addition to rings of recoil.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • In the original version of The Fremennik Trials featured in the RuneScape 2 beta, he had the name Thorvald with the examine "A viking hero."
  • Thorvald's name may come from the Norse explorer Thorvald.
  • Thorvald is also a possible Fremennik name for a player.
